<subSubSection pageId="152" pageNumber="550" type="activity">
<paragraph blockId="152.[166,1375,298,569]" pageId="152" pageNumber="550">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[167,409,298,331]" pageId="152" pageNumber="550">Activity patterns.</emphasis>
Montane Mouse Shrews are terrestrial and mostly nocturnal, although some specimens have been taken during the day.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection box="[168,1108,382,411]" pageId="152" pageNumber="550" type="biology_ecology">
