</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="152" pageNumber="550" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="152.[166,1375,298,569]" pageId="152" pageNumber="550">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[169,514,417,450]" pageId="152" pageNumber="550">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Endangered on The IUCN Red List. The Montane Mouse Shrew is rare and has a very restricted range.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
